With compensation for the girl's family, the agency will not wait for the verdict of the court, but financial compensation is also expected from the culprit.
Amendment of the law?
Not in sight
Clarification of the movement of stewards on board the bus could be brought by an amendment to the law, on which a thirty-member expert group of the Ministry of Transport has been working for over a year.
"However, it did not come to any concrete conclusion.
