The performance also includes music and guitars by Jesús Torres and Paco Arriaga, as well as vocals by Miguel Ortega, el Pulga and Moi de Morón; El Pajar's drums, Raf El Viola's viola and the collaboration of actor Juanfra Juárez, "who has the role of eternal guide of this kind of female artists who are prima donnas with all the trimmings and who are always in love with them".
